The basic concept
    This package is for breakpoint debugging.

The features list
    Please, read the file level document block of "PEAR/BreakpointDebugging.php".

The dependences
    Linux or Windows.
    PHP >= 5.3.0
    You require "shmop" extension if you use "BreakpointDebugging_LockByShmop" class. (optional)
    You require environment which flock() enables if you use "BreakpointDebugging_LockByFlock" class. (optional)

Notice
	I will do execution check of remote debug by rental server.

Warning
    This package version is development.
